<section class="pb-16 pt-8">
  <div class="grid items-center gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr]">
    <div>
      <p class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sky-700">
        SaaS websites that sell clearly
      </p>
      <h1 class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-5xl font-black leading-tight tracking-tight text-slate-950 md:text-6xl">
        Turn a forgettable SaaS site into a sharper growth engine.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
        We help SaaS companies clarify positioning, elevate trust, and launch premium web experiences that feel credible to buyers and simple for teams to manage.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <%= link_to "Book a strategy call", contact_path, class: "rounded-full bg-slate-950 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-xl shadow-slate-300 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-800" %>
        <%= link_to "Explore services", services_path, class: "rounded-full border border-slate-300 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:border-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-50" %>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 grid max-w-2xl gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/70 bg-white/70 p-5 shadow-lg shadow-slate-200/70 backdrop-blur">
          <p class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-950">6 weeks</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Typical launch timeline with weekly decision checkpoints.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/70 bg-white/70 p-5 shadow-lg shadow-slate-200/70 backdrop-blur">
          <p class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-950">3 layers</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Strategy, design, and build delivered as one connected system.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/70 bg-white/70 p-5 shadow-lg shadow-slate-200/70 backdrop-blur">
          <p class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-950">100%</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Custom layouts, no recycled templates or manipulative conversion gimmicks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
      <div class="absolute -right-10 -top-10 h-28 w-28 rounded-full bg-amber-300/70 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute -left-8 bottom-8 h-24 w-24 rounded-full bg-sky-300/70 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-white/70 bg-slate-950 p-6 text-white shadow-2xl shadow-slate-400/40">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/10 pb-4">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-sky-300">Live project board</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-xl font-bold">Website relaunch sprint</p>
          </div>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-400/15 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-300">On track</span>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white/8 p-5">
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Positioning focus</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold">Clarify the product story for technical and commercial buyers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-400 to-cyan-300 p-5 text-slate-950">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em]">Messaging</p>
              <p class="mt-3 text-2xl font-black">Crisp headline system</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-800">Built to support SEO, ads, and sales enablement in one voice.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white/8 p-5">
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Launch assets</p>
              <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-100">
                <li>Homepage narrative</li>
                <li>Service-led landing pages</li>
                <li>Trust and compliance blocks</li>
                <li>Editable SEO panel</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="grid gap-6 pb-16 lg:grid-cols-3">
  <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-white/70 bg-white/75 p-8 shadow-lg shadow-slate-200/70">
    <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-sky-700">Why teams hire us</p>
    <h2 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-black text-slate-950">Websites that look premium and explain the product fast.</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">Buyers do not need more noise. They need clearer offers, stronger proof, and a journey that reduces hesitation.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-950 p-8 text-white shadow-xl shadow-slate-300/30">
    <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-amber-300">What we improve</p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-2xl font-black">Messaging hierarchy, page speed, trust signals, and qualified lead intent.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-white/70 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-200 to-orange-100 p-8 shadow-lg shadow-amber-200/60">
    <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-orange-800">How it feels</p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-2xl font-black text-slate-950">Like your product finally has a website that matches the ambition behind it.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pb-16">
  <div class="rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/70 bg-white/70 p-8 shadow-lg shadow-slate-200/70 lg:p-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-sky-700">Featured capabilities</p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-black text-slate-950 md:text-4xl">Everything your SaaS site needs to convert without feeling pushy.</h2>
      </div>
      <%= link_to "See the full service stack", services_path, class: "rounded-full border border-slate-300 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:border-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-50" %>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-slate-200 p-6">
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-950">Positioning workshops</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">Clarify who you serve, what makes the offer different, and how to describe it in buyer language.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-slate-200 p-6">
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-950">Conversion-led UX</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">Build paths that guide visitors from curiosity to confidence with scannable, accessible layouts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-slate-200 p-6">
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-950">SEO foundations</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">Ship semantic structure, editable metadata, and content blocks that support discoverability without keyword stuffing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-slate-200 p-6">
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-950">Launch support</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">Coordinate QA, redirects, analytics planning, and content reviews so go-live feels controlled, not chaotic.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pb-8">
  <div class="rounded-[2.5rem] bg-slate-950 px-8 py-10 text-white shadow-2xl shadow-slate-300/30 lg:px-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sky-300">Simple next step</p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-black md:text-4xl">If your website undersells your product, we should fix that.</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-300">Share your current site, timeline, and growth goal. We will recommend the clearest path forward.</p>
      </div>
      <%= link_to "Start the conversation", contact_path, class: "rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
